* Old English {{term|heah|hēah|of great height, tall}} <{{proto|Germanic|kaukhaz}} < {{proto|Indo-European|kowkos|hill}} +
* Old English {{term|weg|weġ|lang=ang|road, path}} < {{proto|Germanic|wegaz}} < {{proto|Indo-European|wegʰ-|to move}}.

